<H1>Incrementer Sample</H1>
<p>Click the button to increment a counter in memcache.<br>
    Current count: {{ count }}<br>
    Last incremented by: {{ who }}<br>
    <form method="POST">
        <label for="who">Your name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="who" id="who">
        <button type="submit">Increment</button>
    </form>
